{
  "stem": "24614.5",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I think that what made him decide that he can hide there a lot of Jews.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And when Mrs.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Brussels decided that she was afraid that somebody again will tell on her, she told Kroll and Blancha-- Blancha was part of it too, And von Oste was part of it too, her husband.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they all decided that it would be OK if we go to Stadion street and live there.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Now, Stadion Street was outside of Antwerp, it's called Hoboken.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we went there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They took us at night, and we went there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And there they filled the house with a lot of strange people, Jews, who had wandered from one place to the other, and just like us were still alive.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "One of them had, I'm sure, lost his mind because he was there, but he didn't know what he was doing.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Used to open the door, used to open a window, what he wasn't allowed to.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And one day, he walked out and never came back.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They must have caught him, the Gestapo.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Some of them just left by themselves.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "There were a lot of times that they brought in a child, young kids, 10, 12, 15.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And the other people didn't want them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "My mother always said, if my child is here, this one has to be here, until they find a place for it.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And I remember quite a few arguments.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I remember once I slept on the steps of the house, because my mother wanted this child to sleep with her, near her, like I used to sleep near her.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Because she was afraid that one of the men or one of the women, somebody there, will get that child out of the house, because that child used to cry a lot.",
      "word_count": 32
    }
  ],
